Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.39,0:00:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.85,0:00:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from the year 2036.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuha...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the time traveler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.61,0:00:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John Titor.
