Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:34.93,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Even the world's billions of heartbeats
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:41.85,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}anata ni wa matataki teido no saji na toukyuu
