Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The year 2036.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world was ruled by SERN...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:02:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An oppressive, totalitarian society, a dystopia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people's freedom was stolen,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they lived like zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who disobeyed was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was part of the resistance,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fighting to free the world from SERN's control.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:45.35,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,To change this dead world...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:51.85,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,...I entered the time machine my father left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to change the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, everything you wrote on @channel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, most of it was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But SERN is a research organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not a ruling body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the net, I told John Titor that many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are Chestnut Rice and Kamehameha?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Titor identified himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it wouldn't be fair not to identify myself, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll identify myself, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was using the handle Hououin Kyouma...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SERN succeeded in developing a time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By becoming the only ones able to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,interfere with the fourth dimension, time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they remade the entire world map.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Makise Kurisu is the person
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who contributed the most to the time machine's development.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's worshipped as the mother of the time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I worked with SERN?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I work with the kind of people who
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,perform human experiments?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happened in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you hated me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what about the future me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe Rintarou is a famous terrorist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Terrorist?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A terrorist who fought SERN.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're both...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,dead in the year 2036.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying something crazy like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and returning to the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:04:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the past, to change that future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To 1975...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1975?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SERN succeeded in developing the time machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,due to the time machine created in 2010, in Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the Phone Microwave?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SERN used a communications monitoring system
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to gather all the information they could on time machines, from around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the first D-mail you sent tripped the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The message I sent in front of the Radio Building?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if we delete the message from SERN's database,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the future will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can go to the beta world line, where SERN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,never successfully created a time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will that save Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should start hacking SERN's database immediately...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:06:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need the IBN 5100 for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My task was to go to 1975,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,find an IBN 5100,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and get it to Okabe Rintarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I stayed too long, looking for my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have gone earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as you can, run.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the midst of an operation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to end the Organization's schemes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a level-70 top-secret mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So stay away from this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're running.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but right now, I'm a lab member, just like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the time machine broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it from when it crashed into the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was an error in calculating the coordinates,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where it appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I arrived, it wasn't broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then when?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had to guess, I'd say that thunderstorm we had...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might have been hit by lightning, or flooded...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I stopped you then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the time leap machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can only use it to go back 48 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get back to that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Kurisu-chan and Suzu-san are with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii said we should have a party to celebrate
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the time machine's completion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru-kun and I went shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said we were done for the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to talk about something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go home for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have the party another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't do anything dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii is worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:08:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the trains stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to repair the time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, go back five hours ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to when the time leap machine was completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From there, go back 48 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To 2:00 PM, on the 11th.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the most time we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish the time machine during those two days,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't, I'll redo those two days as many times as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't to save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mission to save Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather all the lab members right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to talk to them about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Future tech is awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be photoshopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Amane, you can't do it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father's the one who made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can fix a time machine
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from 2036, using today's technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't know until we try.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, try and do it in two days, Daru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're our only hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why two days?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:10:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can, I'll do anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher, I want to have a day-long date with Feyris-tan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll make it happen somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're serious? For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more thing, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I fix it, in addition to the IBN 5100,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,get me a cel from the legendary
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1975 magical girl anime, {\i1}Ragical Girl Omit-chan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I help, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you need to finish the time leap machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should get back to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:50.27,Default-alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, aren't you all forgetting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for Suzu-san's dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got in the time machine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you had a job to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but also because you wanted to see your dad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Mayushii wants to help you find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad's name was Barrel Titor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was his code name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know his real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Amane?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My only clue is this little badge he had.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad is in 2010 Akihabara, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Mayushii will be the investigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina Mayuri... She's a good girl, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think you can fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way to say for sure yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I looked at it, I realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of like the Phone Microwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's possible you can fix it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if your dad's nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He knew that we were in Akiba, in 2010, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I never heard from him directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was in his will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad was researching a time machine, \Nseparately from SERN...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To change the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to carry on, in his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it might be that, if I can fix the time machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll find your dad before you get back from 1975.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So keep this a secret from Okarin,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and try to get me that cel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty straightforward way to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly, we're the future gadget lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you don't have a more futuristic way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing so convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Future Gadget #2, Alt. Edition,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Version 2.67.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AKA The Bamboo Copter Camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a CCD camera on the lower body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprisingly sane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:33.81,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Could we use this for an aerial search?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:35.52,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,The camera spins, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:38.35,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,so the video you receive revolves at a high speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:41.81,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,You're at version 2.67, and that still isn't fixed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.19,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first one we've made.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:46.90,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru came up with the name, along with the version.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no real meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Daru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still there, working.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Divergence Meter...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made it. I think you should have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this number goes above 1%, the future will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who will know,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with your Reading Steiner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I give you that, before I died in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I've never met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were a founding member of the resistance I was in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I founded a resistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even save Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I kept on living!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acting like a stupid little kid, with his fantasies?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an honest, brave desire to save the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am mad scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonuvabitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Japanese works, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever seen this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know where it came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you look into it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. It is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure about that Japanese working?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you remember, contact me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this will be created in the near future,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but doesn't exist now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be fated to not meet my dad, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to give up on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're giving up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so mad{\fscx80}-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to prioritize saving Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, you're a lab member and a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help you if I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why are you already giving up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't yell at me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:55.92,Default-alt,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a kidnapping yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the criminal. He wore a badge like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Mayushii's idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think everyone might go, "Huh?" when they see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is operation:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Victory with Mayushii's Pamphlets!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think a kidnapping is going too far, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if the police start looking at us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,474)}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:47.23,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, ask me about these operations first,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:49.56,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,including the name...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:56.32,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.78,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Christina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:01.20,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.91,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned something really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I went to buy lunch, I overheard the clerks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane-san's dad might be a kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were awesome, you would've brought me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an ice-cold zero-calorie cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we fix the time machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even working this whole time, that's still amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru's the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he looks unhealthy and kind of dim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't judge him by his looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I've changed my mind about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you help me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:20:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, in the steaming hot confines of the time machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can forget our shame and take off our clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru-kun and Suzu-san look good together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know how to say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri was just saying something weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if the time machine gets fixed,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about Suzu-san when she rides it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were for two, I could go with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you go with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why else?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd hold Suzu-san's hand really tight, and I'd say,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's okay! Mayushii's with you, so it's okay!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm saying this because
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'll ever have the chance to say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's an exaggeration.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really grateful to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:21:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first came here, I didn't know anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though this era is much more peaceful,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,somehow, to me, it was really scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I have lots of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really happy that I could come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I could spend time with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I could be a lab member, just for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I could spend time with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuha...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.47,0:21:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe Rintarou! Change the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it a free world, like this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mad scientist so cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy from this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that pin badge from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.00,0:21:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found her father?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:21:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:21:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!

